rows.label: qst400101_msg0002

thing we talked about before?

rows.label: qst400101_msg0003

money to purchase?

rows.label: qst400101_msg0004

Can I have a look?

rows.label: qst400101_msg0005
rows.name:

rows.name:
I've taken on a big job direct from
the Chairman. I got 100,000G
just from the advance payment!

rows.label: qst400101_msg0008
rows.name:
But I'll be going into uncharted waters,
so I want to make sure I'm prepared.

rows.label: qst400101_msg0009
rows.name:
This accessory sure to protect Rex!
Shynini guarantee.
